<div style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #111827;">
  <h2 style="color:#111827;margin-top:0;">Your appointment is completed</h2>

  <p>Hi {{#if patientName}}{{patientName}}{{else}}there{{/if}},</p>

  <p>
    Your appointment with
    <strong>{{#if doctorName}}{{doctorName}}{{else}}your doctor{{/if}}</strong>
    for
    <strong>{{appointmentDateTime}}</strong>
    has been marked as
    <strong>completed</strong>.
  </p>

  {{#if appointmentNumber}}
    <p>
      Your appointment number was
      <strong>{{appointmentNumber}}</strong>.
    </p>
  {{/if}}

  <p>
    Thank you for using Remedy. If you have any follow-up questions or need
    another appointment, you can book again through the portal.
  </p>

  <p style="color:#6b7280;margin-top:18px;">Best regards,<br />The Remedy Team</p>
</div>